wikipedia_page.main: George David Panayi (born 23 September 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Warwickshire in the 2017 County Championship on 26 June 2017. He made his List A debut for Warwickshire against the West Indies A team in a tri-series warm-up match on 17 June 2018.
